{"tid":243010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[抵撚死（口德分-10）］楊婉儀開辦，「雙非優先」幼稚園執笠","createTime":"2017-05-14T10:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-14T14:56:45.000Z","uid":48083,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8494c810c0776d8059d80f318d21be3666d8707f","tid":243010,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"前港姐冠軍楊婉儀與丈夫及其他生意伙伴合資開辦，講明「關注雙非童長途跋涉跨境讀書」，標榜優先安排雙非兒童就讀的Golden Gate國際幼稚園暨幼兒園，原來新年後已結業，據指幼稚園涉及不少金錢糾紛。<br />\n <br />\n但幼稚園結業未有打擊楊婉儀辦學的雄心，她指將與美國太空總署（NASA）合作辦學，取名「STEAM」，似乎十分強調科學方面的傳授。"},{"pid":"a791d086f9617fd50d3d09e2d29fd3e7a7c089fd","tid":243010,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"604bb4a768ffe6963670ce66f785627d05ed506c","tid":243010,"uid":1821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:53:22.000Z","msg":"Sperm?"},{"pid":"66cc57e66166252c5f3a139c731f31559c9eba41","tid":243010,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:54:36.000Z","msg":"正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7642a7ba89e9ebed08d0f207e53fd8534da31ce","tid":243010,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:55:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=7662\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D7662&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiuhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=a88caa9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=7662</a>"},{"pid":"90f504e04270d38e22342827ed94ec5c92335002","tid":243010,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T10:57:32.000Z","msg":"nasa係咪俾佢坤左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d139071c4e768f0af7b3cef43ed34469836bbf1","tid":243010,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:04:17.000Z","msg":"生壞腦嘅八婆"